HEADWORD: Feathery
<hw>Feath"er*y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to, or
resembling, feathers; covered with, or as with, feathers; <as>as,
<ex>feathery</ex> spray or snow</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Ye <qex>feathery</qex> people of mid air.</q> <rj><qau>Barry
Cornwall.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Featly</ent>⟦br⟧
